-- Yahoo Names New Chiefs for News, Finance Web Portals
-- B y   B r i a n   W o m a c k
-- 2012-07-18T16:09:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-18/yahoo-names-new-chiefs-for-news-finance-web-portals.html
Yahoo! Inc. named Hillary Frey
editor-in-chief of Yahoo! News and Aaron Task editor-in-chief of
Yahoo! Finance.  “I am thrilled to announce Hillary and Aaron in their new
roles,” said Robertson Barrett, vice president of news and
finance for Yahoo, in the statement. Frey joined Yahoo in 2011
as managing editor for news. Task came to the company in 2008
from The Street.com.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Brian Womack in  San Francisco  at 
